Key Match Events: Idana C. scored an own goal in the 22nd minute.
Kaonga C. equalized for Malawi in the 31st minute.
Girumugisha J. scored for Burundi in the 33rd minute.
Eldhino M. equalized for Malawi in the 59th minute.
Ndayishimiye Y. scored the winning goal for Burundi in the 90+4th minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match ended with a final score of 3-2 in favor of Burundi.
The match took place at Bingu National Stadium in Lilongwe with a capacity of 41,100.
The referee for the match was Traore K. (Ivo).
